The daughter of the Minister of Defense of the Russian Federation, Ksenia Shoigu, brought humanitarian aid to the residents of the DPR: - The Makeyevka sports center “Sport for All” received equipment for football, volleyball, basketball, table tennis, chess, darts, a treadmill and an exercise bike;

— Zugres boarding school No. 31 for children with disabilities received various equipment for traveling to competitions;

— The Amvrosievsky rehabilitation center for combat veterans received a special car with a lift. Subscribe | Suggest news

Forwarded from: Patriot Park, Western Military District
📸Patriot Park of the Western Military District announces the start of a photography competition dedicated to the 320th anniversary of the founding of Kronstadt! The competition is held in 3 stages:
1. Acceptance of works until April 22 at patriot_zvo@mil.ru;
2. The results will be summed up by April 29;
3. May 18, the day of the 320th anniversary of Kronstadt, solemn awarding of the competition winners.

We invite everyone to participate! You can familiarize yourself with the conditions of the competition in the Regulations.

