🇷🇺Health to everyone, dear PEOPLE OF RUSSIA🇷🇺Greetings to the PEOPLE OF RUSSIA channel from 155 GvoBrMP and gratitude for the prompt delivery of everything that the soldiers sent in the order + diesel generator✊🏼COLLECTION #17 had to be divided into several parts, because We have a problem with transport and we have to deliver everything as it turns out. Time does not wait and we also try to do everything as quickly as possible.

Now our 17th COLLECTION has already delivered:
- 5 diesel generators;
- emergency 2 gasoline generators;
- repair kits;
- batteries;
- screwdrivers, impact wrenches, grinders;
- petrol tools;
- consumables (chains, gloves, oils, paints, napkins, towels, etc.);
- mask networks;
- stoves;
- chevrons (order);
- welding equipment;
- radio equipment;
- shoes, clothes, socks;
- wheels for grinders;
- rubber.
It seems like I didn’t forget anything, but I could have forgotten, because... there is a lot, a lot of work and ahead of us is the final shipment for COLLECTION #17 and we are starting a new, Easter, collection.

Bow to all of you, dear friends 🙏🏼Thank you for your constant contribution to the common cause, for your support and help. Together we are POWER!💪🏼GATHERING#17 “Spring”🍃Friends of the channel, comrades-in-arms and like-minded people:
