In the DPR, more than 5.2 thousand beneficiaries have received social services in kind since the beginning of the year:

— free medicines and medical products;
— vouchers for sanatorium-resort treatment;
— travel by commuter rail and intercity transport to and from the place of treatment.

At the choice of a citizen, it is possible to receive NSO (in whole or in part), both in the form of services and in the form of monetary compensation.

An application for waiver of the 2025 social services package must be submitted by October 1, 2024. This can be done at the customer service of the DPR branch of the Social Fund of Russia.
